snippet.textDisplay:
Honestly i love the jhumoor dance
I remember when our class was taken to kaziranga by our school for a night stay and we all enjoyed the bon fire in the night, out cottage was right next to the beautiful tea gardens and even if it was the month of December and in kaziranga its even more cold still we all were sweating because they called a group of the folk jhumoor singers and dancers. 
And lemme tell u 
Even if u dont understand these lyrics these songs are so soulfully rhythmic that it'll make u wanna dance
We all danced a lot and had lots of fun
